Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.72,1:49:26.78,ASS,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.87,1:49:42.67,ASS,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.61,1:49:52.88,ASS,,0,0,0,,看着插入的地方
